{
  "stem": "21550.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They started-- they never-- everything they did was gradually.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They did everything gradually.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't tell you, they-- we gonna-- gonna kill you, although there were signs all over that the Jews are the source of all the evil, that whatever-- whatever-- whatever went wrong was the Jews' fault.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And little by little, we found out that those are the boundaries of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one day, when the walls were put up, they-- so they said, you all go into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody has to move into the ghetto, and you can't go out unless you have a special permission from the Germans.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember I had a cousin who was quite successful in exporting poultry to Spain, Portugal.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he had the permission to leave the ghetto, to go out on business from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the-- one day, he came to the border, to the gate, and he showed his ID to the gendarme.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he looked at him and says, Herr.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You are not a sir.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You are a Jew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he took the ID and tore it into pieces and dropped it on the ground.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You couldn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You couldn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They would-- they would take off Jews-- take off the trains.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They would take them out from-- from public transportation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were without any rights.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were not only second-rate citizens, we were no citizens at all.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't have anything-- anything whatsoever to-- to-- to do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they started with-- the first thing, as soon as they occupied the city, they issued a proclamation that you're not supposed to have any radios, any way of communicating with the outside world.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We have to deliver all the radios.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You-- you had to deliver all the furs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Jews were not allowed to own furs.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
